    // Caller Info: Role-> SUPER_SAFE, Type -> SAFE, Hierarchy -> Squad, Name -> safeSquadA1
    // Target Info: Type-> SAFE, Name -> safeSubSquadA1, Hierarchy related to caller -> DENY_LIST
